      <span class="text-granite-gray lh-copy">We connect Investors with pioneering Enterprenurs. We believe that diversity is key to innovation. </span>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-granite-gray w-80 center pb1">
      <h1 class="text-orange f2 pv1">Why Are We ?</h1>
      <p class="near-white lh-copy">Israel is a startup nation. But its Arab community is severely under-represented in high tech. This is due to lack of dunding and visibility, as well as cultural stereoptypes.
      Fortunately, times are changing. There's a lot of talent to encourage out there.</p>
